<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es"><head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Inscripción de Alumnos · CONAMAT</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin="">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;800&display=swap">
<style>
:root{
  --navy:#1a2e5a; --navy-2:#13234a; --navy-3:#0e1b3a;
  --brand:#2b50a8; --brand-2:#3a63c0;
  --navy-soft:#eef1f8; --navy-soft-2:#dfe5f3; --navy-line:#c9d3ea;
  --green:#1f9d57; --green-soft:#e6f6ed; --green-line:#a7e0c0; --green-press:#178049;
  --red:#d8392b; --red-soft:#fdeeec; --red-line:#f3b9b2;
  --blue-info:#1a56db; --blue-info-soft:#eaf1fe; --blue-info-line:#bcd4fb;
  --amber:#b06a00; --amber-soft:#fdf3e3; --amber-line:#f0d49b;
  --bg:#eef0f5; --surface:#fff; --surface-2:#f7f8fb; --surface-3:#f0f2f7;
  --readonly-bg:#eef1f8;
  --border:#e3e7ef; --border-strong:#cfd6e4;
  --text:#16203a; --text-2:#54607c; --text-3:#8a93a9;
  --r-sm:8px; --r-md:11px; --r-lg:16px; --r-xl:22px;
  --shadow-sm:0 1px 2px rgba(20,30,60,.06);
  --shadow-md:0 6px 22px -6px rgba(20,30,60,.14),0 2px 6px -2px rgba(20,30,60,.07);
  --shadow-lg:0 28px 64px -22px rgba(15,27,58,.40),0 10px 24px -12px rgba(15,27,58,.18);
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;}
body{
  font-family:"Plus Jakarta Sans",system-ui,sans-serif;
  background:var(--bg);
  background-image:linear-gradient(180deg,#e7edfa 0%, var(--bg) 480px);
  background-repeat:no-repeat; background-attachment:fixed;
  color:var(--text);
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;
  font-size:15px; line-height:1.5;
}
.mono{font-family:"JetBrains Mono",ui-monospace,monospace;}
::selection{background:var(--navy-soft-2);}
*::-webkit-scrollbar{width:11px;height:11px;}
*::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#c2cadb;border-radius:99px;border:3px solid transparent;background-clip:content-box;}
*::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover{background:#a9b3c9;background-clip:content-box;}

/* ===== Header ===== */
.topbar{
  background:#fff; color:var(--navy);
  position:sticky; top:0; z-index:30;
  border-top:3px solid var(--brand);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  box-shadow:0 2px 14px -6px rgba(15,27,58,.22);
}
.topbar-in{max-width:920px; margin:0 auto; padding:13px 24px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px;}
.logo-img{height:46px; width:auto; display:block; flex:0 1 auto; min-width:0; max-width:62%; object-fit:contain;}
.topbar .tag{margin-left:auto;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand-2),var(--navy));padding:8px 15px;border-radius:99px;border:0;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;box-shadow:0 4px 12px -3px rgba(43,80,168,.5);}
.topbar .tag .dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:99px;background:#4ade80;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(74,222,128,.25);}
@media(max-width:560px){.topbar .tag{font-size:11px;padding:6px 11px;} .logo-img{height:34px;}}

/* ===== Layout ===== */
.wrap{max-width:920px; margin:0 auto; padding:26px 24px 80px;}

/* progress rail (sticky mini) */
.progress-rail{position:sticky; top:73px; z-index:20; background:#e9eefa; padding:14px 0 6px; margin:-26px 0 0;}
.progress-bar{height:6px;background:var(--surface-3);border-radius:99px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px var(--border);}
.progress-fill{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--navy),#3554a0);border-radius:99px;transition:width .4s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.3,1);width:0;}
.progress-meta{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:7px;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-2);}
.progress-meta b{color:var(--navy);font-weight:700;}

/* intro */
.intro{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);padding:24px 26px;margin:14px 0 22px;display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:flex-start;}
.intro .ic{width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green);display:grid;place-items:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.intro h1{font-size:21px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:0 0 5px;}
.intro p{margin:0;color:var(--text-2);font-size:14.5px;}
.intro p b{color:var(--text);font-weight:700;}

/* ===== Section cards ===== */
.section{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);margin-bottom:18px;overflow:hidden;scroll-margin-top:150px;}
.sec-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:20px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.sec-num{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:99px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand-2),var(--navy));color:#fff;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;flex-shrink:0;transition:all .25s;box-shadow:0 4px 10px -4px rgba(43,80,168,.5);}
.section.complete .sec-num{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2fb56a,var(--green-press));color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 10px -4px rgba(31,157,87,.5);}
.sec-titles{flex:1;min-width:0;}
.sec-title{font-size:16.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.01em;}
.sec-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:1px;}
.sec-status{flex-shrink:0;}
.sec-body{padding:24px;}

/* ===== Grid & fields ===== */
.grid{display:grid;gap:18px;}
.c2{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
.c3{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;}
.c4{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);}
.span2{grid-column:span 2;}
.span-all{grid-column:1/-1;}
@media(max-width:680px){
  .c2,.c3,.c4{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .span2{grid-column:auto;}
}
@media(min-width:681px) and (max-width:840px){
  .c3,.c4{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
}

.field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-width:0;}
.field>label{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-2);margin-bottom:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.field .req{color:var(--red);font-weight:700;}
.optional{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--text-3);font-weight:500;margin-left:auto;}

.ctrl{
  height:46px;border:1.5px solid var(--border-strong);background:var(--surface);
  border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:0 13px;font-family:inherit;font-size:14.5px;color:var(--text);
  width:100%;transition:border-color .14s,box-shadow .14s,background .14s;
}
select.ctrl{appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none;cursor:pointer;padding-right:40px;}
.ctrl::placeholder{color:var(--text-3);}
.ctrl:hover:not(:disabled):not(:focus){border-color:#aab4c8;}
.ctrl:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--brand);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(43,80,168,.16);}
.ctrl:disabled{background:var(--surface-3);color:var(--text-3);cursor:not-allowed;opacity:.7;}
/* Todos los campos de texto en MAYÚSCULAS, excepto los correos. */
input.ctrl:not([type="email"]){text-transform:uppercase;}
input.ctrl:not([type="email"])::placeholder{text-transform:none;}
.input-wrap:has(.ctrl:disabled) .lead{opacity:.5;}

.input-wrap{position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;}
.input-wrap .lead{position:absolute;left:13px;color:var(--text-3);pointer-events:none;display:grid;place-items:center;}
.input-wrap.has-lead .ctrl{padding-left:40px;}
.input-wrap .trail{position:absolute;right:13px;display:grid;place-items:center;}
.select-wrap{position:relative;}
.select-wrap .caret{position:absolute;right:14px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);pointer-events:none;color:var(--text-3);}

/* states */
.field.valid .ctrl{border-color:var(--green-line);}
.field.valid .ctrl:focus{box-shadow:0 0 0 4px var(--green-soft);}
.field.error .ctrl{border-color:var(--red);background:var(--red-soft);}
.field.error .ctrl:focus{box-shadow:0 0 0 4px var(--red-soft);}
.tick{color:var(--green);}
.cross{color:var(--red);}
.hint{font-size:12.5px;margin-top:6px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;line-height:1.4;min-height:0;}
.hint.err{color:var(--red);}
.hint.ok{color:var(--green);}
.hint.muted{color:var(--text-3);}
.ini-warn{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--red);margin-top:6px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;line-height:1.4;}
.ini-warn svg{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
.block-title{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.03em;}
.modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:50;background:rgba(15,27,58,.55);backdrop-filter:blur(2px);display:grid;place-items:center;padding:20px;animation:fadeUp .2s ease;}
.modal-card{background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--r-xl);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);padding:30px 28px;max-width:420px;width:100%;text-align:center;animation:pop .35s cubic-bezier(.2,1.3,.4,1);}
.modal-card .modal-ic{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:99px;margin:0 auto 18px;background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber);display:grid;place-items:center;}
.modal-card h3{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:0 0 10px;}
.modal-card p{margin:0 0 22px;color:var(--text-2);font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.5;}
.modal-card .btn{width:100%;height:48px;}
.modal-card.wide{max-width:540px;text-align:left;}
.modal-card.wide h3{font-size:19px;}
.modal-sub{margin:0 0 16px;color:var(--text-2);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;}
.confirm-table-wrap{max-height:48vh;overflow:auto;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-md);}
.confirm-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13.5px;}
.confirm-table th,.confirm-table td{text-align:left;padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);vertical-align:top;}
.confirm-table th{width:38%;color:var(--text-2);font-weight:600;background:var(--surface-2);white-space:nowrap;}
.confirm-table td{color:var(--text);font-weight:600;}
.confirm-table tr:last-child th,.confirm-table tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}
.modal-actions{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:20px;}
.modal-actions .btn{flex:1;width:auto;height:48px;font-size:15px;}
.btn-ghost{background:var(--surface);border:1.5px solid var(--border-strong);color:var(--text);}
.btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--surface-2);}

/* readonly / RENAPO */
.ro{
  min-height:46px;background:var(--readonly-bg);border:1.5px solid var(--navy-line);
  border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:11px 13px;font-size:14.5px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.ro.empty{color:var(--text-3);font-weight:400;font-style:normal;}
.field.ro-field>label{color:var(--text-3);}
.renapo-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);background:var(--navy-soft-2);padding:3px 8px;border-radius:6px;}

/* big CURP field */
.curp-field .ctrl{height:58px;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:.1em;font-weight:600;text-align:center;}
.curp-field .ctrl::placeholder{letter-spacing:.06em;font-size:16px;}
.renapo-status{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin-top:12px;font-size:13.5px;padding:11px 14px;border-radius:var(--r-md);font-weight:600;}
.renapo-status.loading{background:var(--navy-soft);color:var(--navy);}
.renapo-status.found{background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green-press);}
.renapo-status.notfound{background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber);border:1px solid var(--amber-line);}

/* spinner */
.spin{animation:spin .8s linear infinite;}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}
.shimmer{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--surface-3) 0%,#eaeef5 50%,var(--surface-3) 100%);background-size:200% 100%;animation:sh 1.1s infinite;border-radius:8px;}
@keyframes sh{0%{background-position:200% 0;}100%{background-position:-200% 0;}}

/* ===== Course cards ===== */
.courses{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
@media(max-width:680px){.courses{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
.course{
  border:1.5px solid var(--border-strong);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:18px;cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .15s;background:var(--surface);position:relative;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
}
.course{transition:transform .15s,box-shadow .15s,border-color .15s,background .15s;}
.course:not(.cerrado):hover{border-color:var(--brand);box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);transform:translateY(-3px);}
.course.cerrado{opacity:.6;cursor:not-allowed;background:var(--surface-3);}
.course.cerrado:hover{border-color:var(--border-strong);box-shadow:none;}
.course.cerrado .radio{display:none;}
.type-badge.cerrado-badge{background:var(--red-soft);color:var(--red);}
.cerrado-msg{margin-top:auto;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px dashed var(--border-strong);font-size:13px;color:var(--red);font-weight:600;}
.course.sel{border-color:var(--brand);background:var(--navy-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(43,80,168,.18),0 10px 24px -12px rgba(43,80,168,.45);}
.course .c-top{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.course .radio{width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:99px;border:2px solid var(--border-strong);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;display:grid;place-items:center;transition:all .15s;}
.course.sel .radio{border-color:var(--navy);}
.course.sel .radio::after{content:"";width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:99px;background:var(--navy);}
.course .c-name{font-size:15.5px;font-weight:700;flex:1;}
.course .c-desc{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--text-2);margin:0 0 10px;}
.course .c-meta{list-style:none;margin:0 0 12px;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;}
.course .c-meta li{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.35;}
.course .c-meta li svg{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;color:var(--navy);opacity:.85;}
.course.sel .c-meta li svg{color:var(--navy);opacity:1;}
.type-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:6px;}
.type-badge.grupo{background:var(--navy-soft-2);color:var(--navy);}
.type-badge.particular{background:#f3e8ff;color:#7c3aed;}

/* horarios pills */
.horarios{margin-top:auto;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px dashed var(--border-strong);}
.course.sel .horarios{border-top-color:var(--navy-line);}
.horarios .hl{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-2);margin-bottom:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;}
.pills{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
.pill{
  font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;padding:11px 16px;border-radius:var(--r-md);cursor:pointer;width:100%;text-align:left;
  border:1.5px solid var(--border-strong);background:var(--surface);color:var(--text-2);transition:all .13s;
}
.pill:hover{border-color:var(--navy);color:var(--navy);}
.pill.sel{background:var(--navy);border-color:var(--navy);color:#fff;}
.particular-msg{margin-top:auto;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px dashed var(--navy-line);display:flex;gap:9px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:13px;color:var(--navy);font-weight:600;}
.particular-msg svg{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}

/* ===== Dropzone ===== */
.dropzone{
  border:2px dashed var(--border-strong);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:30px 24px;text-align:center;
  cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;background:var(--surface-2);
}
.dropzone:hover{border-color:var(--navy);background:var(--navy-soft);}
.dropzone.drag{border-color:var(--navy);background:var(--navy-soft);transform:scale(1.005);}
.dropzone .dz-ic{width:54px;height:54px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--navy-soft);color:var(--navy);display:grid;place-items:center;margin:0 auto 14px;}
.dropzone .dz-t{font-weight:700;font-size:15px;}
.dropzone .dz-t b{color:var(--navy);}
.dropzone .dz-d{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:5px;}
.filechip{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:14px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--green-line);background:var(--green-soft);border-radius:var(--r-md);}
.filechip .fc-ic{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:#fff;color:var(--green);display:grid;place-items:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.filechip .fc-meta{flex:1;min-width:0;}
.filechip .fc-name{font-weight:700;font-size:14px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.filechip .fc-size{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-2);}
.filechip .fc-x{background:none;border:0;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-3);padding:6px;border-radius:8px;display:grid;place-items:center;}
.filechip .fc-x:hover{background:rgba(0,0,0,.05);color:var(--red);}

/* ===== Toggle / invoice ===== */
.toggle-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:18px 24px;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;}
.switch{width:46px;height:26px;border-radius:99px;background:var(--border-strong);position:relative;transition:background .18s;flex-shrink:0;}
.switch::after{content:"";position:absolute;top:2px;left:2px;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:99px;background:#fff;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);transition:transform .18s;}
.switch.on{background:var(--navy);}
.switch.on::after{transform:translateX(20px);}
.toggle-row .tt{flex:1;}
.toggle-row .tt b{font-weight:700;font-size:15px;display:block;}
.toggle-row .tt span{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);}
.invoice-body{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:24px;}
.invoice-body.hidden{display:none;}

/* ===== Info banner ===== */
.info-banner{
  background:var(--blue-info-soft);border:1px solid var(--blue-info-line);border-radius:var(--r-lg);
  padding:18px 20px;display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;margin:4px 0 22px;
}
.info-banner .ib-ic{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:10px;background:#fff;color:var(--blue-info);display:grid;place-items:center;flex-shrink:0;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);}
.info-banner .ib-t{font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#16306e;margin-bottom:2px;}
.info-banner .ib-d{font-size:13.5px;color:#2c4582;line-height:1.5;}

/* ===== Submit ===== */
.submit-bar{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;align-items:stretch;}
.btn{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;height:54px;padding:0 26px;
  border-radius:var(--r-md);font-family:inherit;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;
  border:1.5px solid transparent;transition:all .14s;white-space:nowrap;
}
.btn:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--navy);outline-offset:2px;}
.btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand-2),var(--navy));color:#fff;box-shadow:0 10px 24px -10px rgba(43,80,168,.6),var(--shadow-md);}
.btn-primary:hover:not(:disabled){background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),var(--navy-2));transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 14px 28px -10px rgba(43,80,168,.65);}
.btn-primary:active:not(:disabled){transform:translateY(0);}
.btn-primary:disabled{background:#aeb6c9;color:#eef0f5;cursor:not-allowed;box-shadow:none;}
.submit-note{text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:7px;}
.submit-note.blocked{color:var(--amber);}

/* missing list */
.missing{background:var(--amber-soft);border:1px solid var(--amber-line);border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:14px 16px;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--amber);}
.missing b{display:block;margin-bottom:6px;color:#8a5300;}
.missing ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px;}
.missing li{margin:2px 0;}

/* ===== Confirmation ===== */
.confirm{max-width:560px;margin:40px auto;text-align:center;animation:fadeUp .4s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1);}
.confirm .big-check{width:96px;height:96px;border-radius:99px;margin:0 auto 24px;background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green);display:grid;place-items:center;animation:pop .5s cubic-bezier(.2,1.3,.4,1);}
.confirm h2{font-size:27px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:0 0 10px;}
.confirm p.lead{color:var(--text-2);font-size:15.5px;margin:0 0 26px;}
.confirm .folio{background:var(--surface);border:1px dashed var(--border-strong);border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:16px 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;margin-bottom:22px;text-align:left;}
.confirm .folio .fk{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.07em;color:var(--text-3);font-weight:700;}
.confirm .folio .fv{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.02em;white-space:nowrap;}
.confirm .reminder{background:var(--blue-info-soft);border:1px solid var(--blue-info-line);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:18px 20px;text-align:left;display:flex;gap:13px;align-items:flex-start;}
.confirm .reminder .ic{color:var(--blue-info);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
.confirm .reminder .t{font-weight:700;color:#16306e;font-size:14.5px;margin-bottom:3px;}
.confirm .reminder .d{font-size:13.5px;color:#2c4582;line-height:1.5;}
@keyframes pop{0%{transform:scale(.5);}60%{transform:scale(1.12);}100%{transform:scale(1);}}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{transform:translateY(10px);}to{transform:none;}}
.fade-in{animation:fadeUp .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1);}

/* footer */
.foot{text-align:center;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:30px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:7px;}

.hidden{display:none !important;}
.divider{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin:20px 0;}
</style>
</head>
<body>



<header class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-in">
    <img class="logo-img" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="CONAMAT · Colegio Nacional de Matemáticas · Plantel Hidalgo - San Cosme">
    <span class="tag"><span class="dot"></span><span class="t">Plantel Hidalgo ·</span> Ciclo 2026 - 2027</span>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ===== FORM VIEW ===== -->
<div id="formView" class="wrap">

  <div class="progress-rail">
    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div></div>
    <div class="progress-meta"><span>Progreso del registro</span><span><b id="progressPct">0%</b> completado</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="intro">
    <div class="ic" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12.5 10 17.5 19.5 7"></path></svg>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h1>Completa tu inscripción</h1>
      <p>Recibimos tu pago por transferencia. <b>Captura tus datos</b> para que el equipo de CONAMAT complete tu registro. Toma unos 3 minutos.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <form id="form" novalidate="" autocomplete="off">

    <!-- 1. IDENTIFICACIÓN -->
    <section class="section" id="sec-ident" data-sec="">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <div class="sec-num">1</div>
        <div class="sec-titles"><div class="sec-title">Identificación</div><div class="sec-desc">La CURP detecta tu fecha de nacimiento y sexo; captura tus apellidos y nombre</div></div>
        <div class="sec-status" data-status=""></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-body">
        <div class="field curp-field" data-field="curp">
          <label for="curp">CURP <span class="req">*</span></label>
          <div class="input-wrap">
            <input class="ctrl mono" id="curp" name="curp" maxlength="18" placeholder="GOGA800101MDFRRN09" inputmode="text" aria-describedby="curp-hint">
            <span class="trail" data-trail=""></span>
          </div>
          <div class="hint muted" id="curp-hint">18 caracteres. Se convierte a mayúsculas automáticamente.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="renapo-status hidden" id="renapoStatus"></div>

        <div id="renapoFields" class="hidden">
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <div class="grid c3">
            <div class="field span-all" style="margin-bottom:-6px"><label>Nombre del alumno <span class="req">*</span></label></div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid c3" style="margin-top:10px">
            <div class="field" data-field="paterno">
              <label for="paterno">Apellido paterno <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="paterno" name="paterno" placeholder="González" autocapitalize="words"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="field" data-field="materno">
              <label for="materno">Apellido materno <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="materno" name="materno" placeholder="García" autocapitalize="words"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="field" data-field="nombre">
              <label for="nombre">Nombre(s) <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Ana" autocapitalize="words"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid c3" style="margin-top:16px">
            <div class="field ro-field span-all" style="margin-bottom:-6px"><label><span class="renapo-badge"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 11V8a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3M5 11h14v9H5z"></path></svg> Derivado de tu CURP</span></label></div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid c3" style="margin-top:10px">
            <div class="field ro-field"><label>Fecha de nacimiento</label><div class="ro empty" data-ro="fechaNac">—</div></div>
            <div class="field ro-field"><label>Sexo</label><div class="ro empty" data-ro="sexo">—</div></div>
            <div class="field ro-field"><label>Edad</label><div class="ro empty" data-ro="edad">—</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2. CONTACTO -->
    <section class="section" id="sec-contacto" data-sec="">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <div class="sec-num">2</div>
        <div class="sec-titles"><div class="sec-title">Contacto</div><div class="sec-desc">Cómo localizarte a ti y dónde vives</div></div>
        <div class="sec-status" data-status=""></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-body">
        <div class="grid c2">
          <div class="field" data-field="celular">
            <label for="celular">Celular <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap has-lead">
              <span class="lead"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 4h3l2 5-2.5 1.5a11 11 0 0 0 5 5L19 12l2 5v3a1 1 0 0 1-1.1 1A16 16 0 0 1 4 5.1 1 1 0 0 1 5 4Z"></path></svg></span>
              <input class="ctrl" id="celular" name="celular" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="14" placeholder="55 0000 0000">
              <span class="trail" data-trail=""></span>
            </div>
            <div class="hint muted">10 dígitos</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="correo">
            <label for="correo">Correo electrónico <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap has-lead">
              <span class="lead"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 5h16v14H4zM4 6.5 12 13l8-6.5"></path></svg></span>
              <input class="ctrl" id="correo" name="correo" type="email" placeholder="nombre@correo.com">
              <span class="trail" data-trail=""></span>
            </div>
            <div class="hint muted"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid c4" style="margin-top:18px">
          <div class="field" data-field="cp">
            <label for="cp">Código postal <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap">
              <input class="ctrl" id="cp" name="cp" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="5" placeholder="06600">
              <span class="trail" data-trail=""></span>
            </div>
            <div class="hint muted">Autollena estado y municipio</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field ro-field"><label>Estado</label><div class="ro empty" data-ro="estado">Se completa con el CP</div></div>
          <div class="field ro-field"><label>Municipio / Alcaldía</label><div class="ro empty" data-ro="municipio">Se completa con el CP</div></div>
          <div class="field" data-field="colonia">
            <label for="colonia">Colonia</label>
            <div class="select-wrap">
              <select class="ctrl" id="colonia" name="colonia" disabled=""><option value="">Ingresa el CP</option></select>
              <span class="caret"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid c4" style="margin-top:18px">
          <div class="field span2" data-field="calle">
            <label for="calle">Calle <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="calle" name="calle" placeholder="Av. Insurgentes Sur"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="numExt">
            <label for="numExt">Núm. exterior <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="numExt" name="numExt" placeholder="123"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="numInt">Núm. interior <span class="optional">opcional</span></label>
            <input class="ctrl" id="numInt" name="numInt" placeholder="4B">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. TUTOR Y EMERGENCIAS -->
    <section class="section" id="sec-tutor" data-sec="">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <div class="sec-num">3</div>
        <div class="sec-titles"><div class="sec-title">Tutor y contacto de emergencia</div><div class="sec-desc">Persona responsable y a quién llamar en caso necesario</div></div>
        <div class="sec-status" data-status=""></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-body">
        <!-- Responsable 1 -->
        <div class="block-title">Responsable 1 <span class="optional" style="font-weight:600;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0">padre, madre o tutor</span></div>
        <div class="grid c2" style="margin-top:12px">
          <div class="field" data-field="resp1Nombre">
            <label for="resp1Nombre">Nombre completo <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="resp1Nombre" placeholder="Nombre completo"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="resp1Parentesco">
            <label for="resp1Parentesco">Parentesco <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="select-wrap">
              <select class="ctrl parentesco" id="resp1Parentesco"></select>
              <span class="caret"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="resp1Tel">
            <label for="resp1Tel">Teléfono <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap has-lead">
              <span class="lead"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 4h3l2 5-2.5 1.5a11 11 0 0 0 5 5L19 12l2 5v3a1 1 0 0 1-1.1 1A16 16 0 0 1 4 5.1 1 1 0 0 1 5 4Z"></path></svg></span>
              <input class="ctrl" id="resp1Tel" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="14" placeholder="55 0000 0000">
              <span class="trail" data-trail=""></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="resp1Correo">
            <label for="resp1Correo">Correo <span class="optional">opcional</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap has-lead">
              <span class="lead"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 5h16v14H4zM4 6.5 12 13l8-6.5"></path></svg></span>
              <input class="ctrl" id="resp1Correo" type="email" placeholder="correo@correo.com">
              <span class="trail" data-trail=""></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <!-- Responsable 2 (opcional) -->
        <div class="block-title">Responsable 2 <span class="optional" style="font-weight:600;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0">opcional</span></div>
        <div class="grid c2" style="margin-top:12px">
          <div class="field" data-field="resp2Nombre">
            <label for="resp2Nombre">Nombre completo</label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="resp2Nombre" placeholder="Nombre completo"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="resp2Parentesco">
            <label for="resp2Parentesco">Parentesco</label>
            <div class="select-wrap">
              <select class="ctrl parentesco" id="resp2Parentesco"></select>
              <span class="caret"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="resp2Tel">
            <label for="resp2Tel">Teléfono</label>
            <div class="input-wrap has-lead">
              <span class="lead"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 4h3l2 5-2.5 1.5a11 11 0 0 0 5 5L19 12l2 5v3a1 1 0 0 1-1.1 1A16 16 0 0 1 4 5.1 1 1 0 0 1 5 4Z"></path></svg></span>
              <input class="ctrl" id="resp2Tel" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="14" placeholder="55 0000 0000">
              <span class="trail" data-trail=""></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="resp2Correo">Correo</label>
            <div class="input-wrap has-lead">
              <span class="lead"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 5h16v14H4zM4 6.5 12 13l8-6.5"></path></svg></span>
              <input class="ctrl" id="resp2Correo" type="email" placeholder="correo@correo.com">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <!-- Salud -->
        <label class="toggle-row" for="enfermedadToggle" style="padding:0">
          <span class="switch" id="enfermedadSwitch"></span>
          <span class="tt"><b>¿Alguna enfermedad o condición médica?</b><span>Actívalo si el alumno tiene alguna condición que debamos conocer</span></span>
          <input type="checkbox" id="enfermedadToggle" class="hidden">
        </label>
        <div id="enfermedadBody" class="hidden" style="margin-top:14px">
          <div class="field" data-field="enfermedadDesc">
            <label for="enfermedadDesc">Descripción <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="enfermedadDesc" placeholder="Describe la enfermedad, alergia o condición"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <!-- Contacto de emergencia (obligatorio, distinto a los responsables) -->
        <div class="block-title">Contacto de emergencia</div>
        <div class="grid c3" style="margin-top:12px">
          <div class="field" data-field="emergNombre">
            <label for="emergNombre">Nombre <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="emergNombre" placeholder="Nombre completo"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="emergParentesco">
            <label for="emergParentesco">Parentesco <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="select-wrap">
              <select class="ctrl parentesco" id="emergParentesco"></select>
              <span class="caret"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="emergTel">
            <label for="emergTel">Teléfono <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap has-lead">
              <span class="lead"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 4h3l2 5-2.5 1.5a11 11 0 0 0 5 5L19 12l2 5v3a1 1 0 0 1-1.1 1A16 16 0 0 1 4 5.1 1 1 0 0 1 5 4Z"></path></svg></span>
              <input class="ctrl" id="emergTel" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="14" placeholder="55 0000 0000">
              <span class="trail" data-trail=""></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. DATOS ACADÉMICOS -->
    <section class="section" id="sec-academico" data-sec="">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <div class="sec-num">4</div>
        <div class="sec-titles"><div class="sec-title">Datos académicos</div><div class="sec-desc">Tu escuela actual y nivel de estudios</div></div>
        <div class="sec-status" data-status=""></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-body">
        <div class="grid c2">
          <div class="field" data-field="escuela">
            <label for="escuela">Escuela de procedencia <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="escuela" name="escuela" list="escuelasList" placeholder="Escribe el número o el nombre…" autocomplete="off"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
            <datalist id="escuelasList"></datalist>
            <div class="hint muted">Escribe el número (ej. 3) o el nombre y elige de la lista. Si no aparece, escríbela completa.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="nivel">
            <label for="nivel">Nivel de estudios <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="select-wrap">
              <select class="ctrl" id="nivel" name="nivel"></select>
              <span class="caret"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg></span>
            </div>
            <div class="hint muted"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5. SELECCIÓN DE CURSO -->
    <section class="section" id="sec-curso" data-sec="">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <div class="sec-num">5</div>
        <div class="sec-titles"><div class="sec-title">Selecciona tu curso</div><div class="sec-desc">Elige el curso y, si aplica, tu horario</div></div>
        <div class="sec-status" data-status=""></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-body">
        <div class="courses" id="courses"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. COMPROBANTE -->
    <section class="section" id="sec-comprobante" data-sec="">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <div class="sec-num">6</div>
        <div class="sec-titles"><div class="sec-title">Comprobante de pago</div><div class="sec-desc">Sube tu comprobante de transferencia</div></div>
        <div class="sec-status" data-status=""></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-body">
        <div id="dropzone" class="dropzone" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Subir comprobante de pago">
          <div class="dz-ic"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 16V4M7 9l5-5 5 5M5 20h14"></path></svg></div>
          <div class="dz-t">Arrastra tu archivo o <b>haz clic para elegir</b></div>
          <div class="dz-d">PDF, JPG o PNG · máximo 5 MB</div>
        </div>
        <input type="file" id="fileComprobante" accept=".pdf,.jpg,.jpeg,.png" class="hidden">
        <div id="comprobanteChip"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 7. FACTURA -->
    <section class="section" id="sec-factura" data-sec="">
      <label class="toggle-row" for="facturaToggle">
        <span class="switch" id="facturaSwitch"></span>
        <span class="tt"><b>Requiero factura</b><span>Actívalo si necesitas comprobante fiscal (CFDI)</span></span>
        <input type="checkbox" id="facturaToggle" class="hidden">
      </label>
      <div class="invoice-body hidden" id="invoiceBody">
        <div class="info-banner" style="margin:0 0 18px">
          <div class="ib-ic"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 21a9 9 0 1 0 0-18 9 9 0 0 0 0 18Zm0-9v5m0-9v.5"></path></svg></div>
          <div>
            <div class="ib-t">Sobre tu factura</div>
            <div class="ib-d">La factura se genera <b>con los datos que captures aquí</b>, así que verifica que estén correctos. Subir tu <b>Constancia de Situación Fiscal no es obligatorio, pero sí muy recomendable</b> para evitar errores. Si la factura sale con un error por datos mal capturados, <b>CONAMAT no se hace responsable</b>.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid c2">
          <div class="field" data-field="rfc">
            <label for="rfc">RFC <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl mono" id="rfc" name="rfc" maxlength="13" placeholder="GOGA800101AB1" style="text-transform:uppercase"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
            <div class="hint muted">12 (moral) o 13 (física) caracteres</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="cpFiscal">
            <label for="cpFiscal">Código postal fiscal <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap"><input class="ctrl" id="cpFiscal" name="cpFiscal" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="5" placeholder="06600"><span class="trail" data-trail=""></span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="regimen">
            <label for="regimen">Régimen fiscal <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="select-wrap">
              <select class="ctrl" id="regimen" name="regimen"><option value="">Selecciona…</option></select>
              <span class="caret"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field" data-field="correoFiscal">
            <label for="correoFiscal">Correo para envío de factura <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap has-lead">
              <span class="lead"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 5h16v14H4zM4 6.5 12 13l8-6.5"></path></svg></span>
